<section id="project" class="project">
  <h2>Final Year Project</h2>
  <h3>Stock Price Prediction Using Machine Learning</h3>

  <div class="project-content">
    <p>
      This project focused on building a <strong>Stock Price Prediction System</strong>
      using <strong>Machine Learning (LSTM)</strong> to forecast Google stock trends
      based on six months of data. The system applies deep learning to model financial
      patterns and predict future stock prices accurately.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Language:</strong> Python</li>
      <li><strong>Libraries:</strong> TensorFlow, Keras, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, scikit-learn</li>
      <li><strong>Algorithm:</strong> Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM)</li>
      <li><strong>Duration:</strong> July – December 2022</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      The model achieved a strong accuracy with a Root Mean Square Error (RMSE)
      of <strong>1.28</strong> during training and <strong>0.83</strong> during testing,
      proving that AI models can effectively analyze and forecast market behavior.
    </p>

    <div class="project-image">
      <img src="img/Chart.jpg" alt="Stock Prediction Chart">
    </div>

    <p class="project-quote">
      “This work shows how artificial intelligence can revolutionize financial forecasting and decision-making.”
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

